# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI Desk Companion — Root environment variables reference
# Each sub-package has its own .env.example with full details:
#
#   apps/orchestrator/.env.example   ← Python FastAPI backend (port 8787)
#   apps/desktop/.env.example        ← Vite/React frontend (port 5173)
#
# Copy the relevant .env.example to a .env file in the same directory.
# Never commit any .env file — they are git-ignored.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Quick-start minimum (orchestrator) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to apps/orchestrator/.env — all other values have working defaults.

# LLM provider key (needed for AI routing and responses):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Smart Home — only if you have Home Assistant:
# MYHOME_MCP_ENDPOINT=http://homeassistant.local:8123
# MYHOME_MCP_TOKEN=eyJ...
